<item>
            <title>[LU-3537] allow cross-MDT for all metadata operations </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3537</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In DNE phase I, only create/unlink remote directories are allowed between MDT. In DNE phase II, all of metadata operation are allowed to be cross-MDT. This task should remove those limitation added in phase I, and add necessary cross-MDT updates to allow all metadata operation to cross-MDT.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
